INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (319,'021','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 brings a fortune like fish leaving a small well to venture into the vast ocean, filled with ambition and vitality. Your household members will harmonize and support each other, creating a peaceful and prosperous home where fortunate and beneficial events never cease. Spring passes peacefully without worries, but summer brings some obstacles. However, like medicinal herbs blooming in season, wealth follows you and unexpected celebrations arrive. Clouds briefly scatter to reveal a bright moon, making heaven and earth clear and cheerful. Worries disappear completely, family harmony prevails, and all matters proceed smoothly. However, you must be cautious in forming relationships and careful to avoid gossip in romantic affairs.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
Your 2026 financial fortune is generally favorable, though first and second half patterns differ. In January and February, blessings descend upon you and wealth naturally flourishes, bringing abundant provisions. February may bring the joy of family expansion or property increase. March shows outward joy but inner concerns, requiring careful investment judgment. In May, avoid hastily planning new ventures and focus on existing business. July brings opportunities to gain wealth from other regions or external sources. August sees small gains accumulating into large profits. September brings benefits from specific sources, leading to financial gains. October is blessed with external income, but beware of gossip. Year-end brings profits through good closure, with western and southern directions being auspicious.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
For professionals, this is a year when harmony between superiors and subordinates earns you virtuous praise from neighbors. In January, vibrant energy reaches your home and displays its power, allowing you to enjoy yourself without worries. The first half generally proceeds smoothly, but April and May bring obstacles requiring patience and careful handling. June and July favor external activities over staying home, so actively move about. Business trips and expeditions are advantageous during this period. In August, heaven and earth harmonize, bringing benefits through cooperation and harmony to achieve results. November requires seeing tasks through to completion once started, avoiding half-finished work. December may bring joy through official positions when you meet benefactors, so pay attention to relationships.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
Romance fortune is good in spring but requires caution from summer onward. January and February are like peach blossoms meeting spring, offering opportunities to meet good matches and bear sincere fruit. Singles may find connections leading to marriage. From March, outward joy contrasts with inner concerns, so avoid misunderstandings in romantic relationships. In July, choosing companions poorly brings disadvantage, so exercise caution in dealings and carefully select partners. October requires treating romantic relationships seriously to avoid gossip. November and December require caution in socializing, but wise conduct can lead to good connections. Married couples maintaining spousal harmony will enjoy peaceful households.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
Health fortune is generally favorable but requires summer management. Spring passes peacefully without worries, bringing mental and physical stability. Summer brings irritations and stress accumulation, requiring sufficient rest and sleep. April and May require avoiding overwork and attending to health management. June and July may accumulate fatigue if traveling, so take appropriate rest. Conditions recover from August onward, with autumn bringing health stability. Year-round stress management is important, with regular exercise and balanced meals being keys to maintaining health. Pay particular attention to digestive and nervous systems, avoiding overeating and excessive drinking.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
This is a year when family harmony forms the foundation of relationships. Household members harmonize and help each other, creating a peaceful and tranquil home. January and February bring harmony between superiors and subordinates, earning good reputation at work and in society. However, from March onward, exercise caution in forming friendships. July brings disadvantage from poor companion choices, so carefully examine potential partners in dealings and cooperation. August brings mutual help from surrounding people, creating peace and tranquility. October makes romantic gossip likely, so avoid rash behavior. November and December reveal that not all people are good, requiring wise discernment in forming friendships. Meeting benefactors brings good opportunities, so work on networking while maintaining vigilance.

âœ¨ 7. ğŸ“š Academic and Self-Development Fortune
